<% content_for :banner do %>
  <div class="inner">
    <h1>PushType manifesto</h1>
    <h2>The PushType mission is to inspire the next generation of Ruby developers with a next generation content management system.</h2>
  </div>
<% end %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="mn-col">
    <div class="mn-body">
      <div class="flag">
        <div class="image">
          <svg class="icon-makers"><use xlink:href="#icon-makers"></use></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <h2>1. We are makers</h2>
          <p>Be creative and embrace your ideas. Think big, start small. Be a hacker and a fixer. Obsessively improve things.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flag">
        <div class="image">
          <svg class="icon-discoverers"><use xlink:href="#icon-discoverers"></use></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <h2>2. We are discoverers</h2>
          <p>Do the things you've never done. Seek different ways. Don't be afraid to fail. Never stop learning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flag">
        <div class="image">
          <svg class="icon-different"><use xlink:href="#icon-different"></use></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <h2>3. We are different</h2>
          <p>Be the crazy one. Nurture your curiosity. Believe in yourself. Don't assume others are never wrong.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flag">
        <div class="image">
          <svg class="icon-community"><use xlink:href="#icon-community"></use></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <h2>4. We are community</h2>
          <p>Embrace our diversity and never discriminate. Reach out and participate. Share your ideas, enthusiasm and skills. Support one another, be friendly and have fun.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flag">
        <div class="image">
          <svg class="icon-rubyists"><use xlink:href="#icon-rubyists"></use></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
          <h2>5. We are Rubyists</h2>
          <p>Enjoy programming and strive to be happy. Write beautiful code. Build wonderful things.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="mn-cta">
    <div class="panel callout success">
      <h3>Support the PushType manifesto</h3>
      <p>Show <strong>your support</strong> by sharing the PushType manifesto:</p>
      <p>
        <a href="<%= share_manifesto_link :twitter %>" target="_blank" class="button twitter"><%= ficon :social_twitter, 'Tweet the manifesto' %></a>
        &nbsp;or&nbsp;
        <a href="<%= share_manifesto_link :facebook %>" target="_blank" class="button facebook"><%= ficon :social_facebook, 'Share the manifesto' %></a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><em>Version: 1.0</em></p>
  </div>
</div>

